nlc prompt system - Show or edit system prompt

[1mUsage:[0m
  nlc prompt system [OPTIONS]
  nlc prompt system --help | -h

[1mOptions:[0m
  [32m--edit, -e[0m
    Open the file for editing

  [32m--default, -d[0m
    Copy the default system prompt to the override file

  [32m--clear, -c[0m
    Delete the prompt override file

  [32m--help, -h[0m
    Show this help

[1mExamples:[0m
  # clone the default config and open for editing"
  nlc prompt system -ed
